(PROJECT OVERVIEW) Tj
0 -14 Td
(This project combines a browser frontend, a Node.js inference helper backend,) Tj
0 -14 Td
(and a Python FastAPI analytics backend for cognitive speech-risk tracking.) Tj
0 -14 Td
