(PRIMARY TECHNOLOGIES) Tj
0 -14 Td
(1\) Frontend: HTML + CSS + Vanilla JavaScript \(components, API integration, recording UI\).) Tj
0 -14 Td
(2\) Node Backend: Express, Axios, Multer, CORS, Dotenv for HF transcription/analysis APIs.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(3\) Python Backend: FastAPI, SQLAlchemy, Librosa, NumPy, SciPy, NLTK for signal + NLP pipeline.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(4\) Storage: SQLite database + filesystem audio uploads.) Tj
