(DATA FLOW) Tj
0 -14 Td
(1\) User creates/signs in account from login modal.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(2\) Frontend calls /api/user and stores backend user_id.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(3\) Recording is captured and converted to WAV in browser.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(4\) Frontend sends WAV + transcript + user_id to /api/upload.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(5\) Backend stores audio, computes features/baseline/drift/CSI, stores session row.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(6\) User-level latest score/session metadata is updated in users table.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(7\) Frontend fetches /api/dashboard/{user_id} for persisted score/trend rendering.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
